reats theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/spa-treats-spa-restaurant-wordpress/3002682" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-149172" alt="alfie" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/spa_treats.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>SPA Theme Designed for spa, salon, health care, medical business, massage center, beauty center. You can customize the look of the site easily via the custom theme options panel.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/spa-treats-spa-restaurant-wordpress/3002682" target="_blank">Purchase SPA Treats</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">GC Message Bar plugin</h2>\n<blockquote><p>GC Message Bar is a simple plugin that allows you to place a sticky message and a Call To Action button to the top or bottom of your website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://wordpress.org/plugins/gc-message-bar" target="_blank">Download GC Message Bar</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:91:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/this-week-compatible-minx-lecia-spa-treats-and-gc-message-bar/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:69:"This week compatible – FooCamp