erce &amp; business websites. Whether you want to sell clothes, electronics, digital items like prints or songs, this theme might just be for you.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/replete-ecommerce-and-business/3519946?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Kriesi" target="_blank">Purchase Replete</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Eunoia theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/eunoia-responsive-portfolio/2792441" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-161815" alt="eunoia" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/eunoia.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Eunoia is a bold responsive theme, suited for business websites and users who want to showcase their work on a neat portfolio site. It comes with theme admin panel so you can modify layout, styling, colors and fonts directly from within the backend.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/eunoia-responsive-portfolio/2792441" target="_blank">Purchase Eunoia</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">907 theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/907-responsive-wp-one-page-parallax/4087140" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-161813" alt="907_theme" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/907_theme.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>907 is a responsive multi-purpose theme suitable for any business (corporate, agency, portfolio and blog websites). Some features of 907 are: revolution slider, google fonts, contact form and header options.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/907-responsive-wp-one-page-parallax/4087140" target="_blank">Purchase 907</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Global gallery plugin</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.projects.lcweb.it/global-gallery" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-161814" alt="global_gallery" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/global_gallery.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Global Gallery allow you to create unlimited responsive galleries fastly with ease. Is designed to be visible on each device: whether you are using a retina MacBook or an Android phone. At the same time it is coded to work also on old browsers like Internet Explorer 8.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.projects.lcweb.it/global-gallery" target="_blank">Purchase gobal gallery</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"http://wpml.org/2013/09/this-week-compatible-replete-eunoia-907-and-global-gallery/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:92:"This week compatible – Rounder, Fairytale, Shop & Buy, GC Message Box and Alfie WP Weather";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:108:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/this-week-compatible-r