>This week the WPML compatibility team would like to introduce you with these fully compatible themes: <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/foocamp-conference-wordpress-theme/4429812" target="_blank">FooCamp</a>, <a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/reportage/" target="_blank">Reportage</a>, <a href="http://www.elegantthemes.com/gallery/convertible/" target="_blank">Convertible</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/myempire-responsive-multipurpose-theme/5027053" target="_blank">MyEmpire</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">FooCamp theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/foocamp-conference-wordpress-theme/4429812/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-153542" alt="foocamp" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/foocamp.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>FooCamp theme is a good solution for anybody who’s organizing a conference or barcamp. Theme has built in features that allow you to easily configure conference program schedule in different rooms and locations, speakers details, FAQ section and nice countdown.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/foocamp-conference-wordpress-theme/4429812" target="_blank">Purchase FooCamp</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Reportage theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/reportage/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-153543" alt="reportage" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/reportage.jpg" width="440" height="268" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Reportage is a clean, sophisticated newspaper-style WordPress theme tailored for news websites, writers, journalists, or professional blogs that has a lot of content. The Reportage WordPress theme integrates elements that a newspaper-style website needs, making it very useful and effective for managing lots of posts on a page.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/reportage/" target="_blank">Purchase Reportage</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Convertible theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.elegantthemes.com/gallery/convertible/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-153541" alt="convertible" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/convertible.jpg" width="590" height="299" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Convertible is a new take on the classic sales page. Landing pages are useful for marketers who have a single product to sell and need to create a page to pitch it to their visitors. Convertible includes a custom Drag and Drop page builder that allows you to completely customize your landing page without ever having to touch a line of code.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.elegantthemes.com/gallery/convertible/" target="_blank">Purchase Convertible</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">MyEmpire theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/myempire-responsive-multipurpose-theme/5027053" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-153545" alt="myempire" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/myempire.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>MyEmpire is a multi-purpose WordPress theme. It comes with a good number of really hand theme options so that you can configure your website with minimum effort and time. The options panel is completely unbranded allowing you to easily add your company name to it.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/myempire-responsive-multipurpose-theme/5027053" target="_blank">Purchase MyEmpire</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:93:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/this-week-compatible-foocamp-reportage-convertible-and-myempire/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"Learn About Working in a Distributed Company";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:69:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/learn-about-working-in-a-distributed-company/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:78:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/learn-about-working-in-a-distributed-company/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 07 Aug 2013 07:30:51 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"news";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"http://wpml.org/?p=152562";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:351:"OnTheGoSystems (our company) is growing and we&#8217;re looking for the best developers out there to join us. We&#8217;ve been operating as a distributed company from day one, sometime back in 2007. When I think about it, I realize that what seems obvious to us, isn&#8217;t quite natural to everyone. Some of the people we&#8217;re interviewing [...]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Amir";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1215:"<p><a href="http://www.onthegosystems.com/">OnTheGoSystems</a> (our company) is growing and we&#8217;re looking for the best developers out there to join us.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve been operating as a distributed company from day one, sometime back in 2007. When I think about it, I realize that what seems obvious to us, isn&#8217;t quite natural to everyone. Some of the people we&#8217;re interviewing now are great developers, but are new to working remotely from home.</p>\n<p>I sat myself down and wrote a page that explains the <a href="http://www.onthegosystems.com/about/is-working-at-home-for-you/">pros and cons of working in remote</a>.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re considering leaving the comforts of your office and starting to work from home, you might get a thing or two from there. The executive summary of that page:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Remote working puts you in charge of your life and gives you all the flexibility you can have.</li>\n<li>You need to learn how to manage yourself, organize your time and life.\n</ul>\n<p>That page is closed for comments, but I&#8217;d love to hear what you think and learn from your experience working from home.</p>\n<p>Leave your comments here and I&#8217;ll get back to you.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/learn-about-working-in-a-distributed-company/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"Now compatible – Franklin, Stardust, CuckooBizz, Coverage and Arthemia";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/now-compatible-franklin-stardust-cuckoobizz-coverage-and-arthemia/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:99:"http://wpml.org/2013/08/now-compatible-franklin-stardust-cuckoobizz-coverage-and-arthemia/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 07 Aug 2013 05:46:01 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Uncategorized";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"http://wpml.org/?p=152475";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:353:"We are happy to announce about another list of themes which are now compatible with WPML, these are: Franklin, Stardust, CuckooBizz, Coverage, Arthemia. If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if you&#8217;re a theme [...]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Dominykas";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6016:"<p>We are happy to announce about another list of themes which are now compatible with WPML, these are: <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" target="_blank">Franklin</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" target="_blank">Stardust</a>, <a href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" target="_blank">CuckooBizz</a>, <a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/coverage/" target="_blank">Coverage</a>, <a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/arthemia-premium/" target="_blank">Arthemia</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Franklin theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152495" alt="franklin" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/franklin.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Franklin is a wordpress crowdfunding theme, elegant and bloat-free. Franklin gives you the ability to crowdfund your latest project in style. Franklin is designed to work both for single-campaign websites and community oriented crowdfunding websites.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" target="_blank">Purchase Franklin</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Stardust theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152478" alt="stardust" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/stardust.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Stardust is a multi-purpose portfolio theme. Some features of Stardust are: mix full-width and standard Grid, interactive elements, unlimited colors and sizes for all elements, 500+ Google fonts and a robust backend offers a solution for a variety of business or personal uses.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" target="_blank">Purchase Stardust</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">CuckooBizz theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152481" alt="cuckoobizz" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/cuckoobizz.jpg" width="580" height="262" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>CuckooBizz theme can be used for creating a one page site, multiple pages site with one page site homepage functionality or ecommerce site. Integrated homepage builder allows creating a unique homepage structure, adding content and customizing the appearance of each homepage unit.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" target="_blank">Purchase CuckooBizz</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Coverage theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/coverage/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Coverage-WPML.png" alt="Coverage-WPML" width="590" height="300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160310" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Coverage is a solution who has a will to make own blog become a news portal. With a nice design and also attractive features readers can freely discover and choose what news they want to read, all posts you have will be organized on every sections which will made anyone enjoy to read your site.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/coverage/" target="_blank">Purchase Coverage</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Arthemia theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/arthemia-premium/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Arthemia-WPML.png" alt="Arthemia-WPML" width="590" height="300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160308" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Arthemia is a magazine-styled theme. With a good number of numerous built-in features, arthemia will convert your old-fashioned WordPress blog to nice front-end.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/arthemia-premium/" target="_blank">Purchase Arthemia</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_ba